JAKARTA, June 9 (Xinhua) -- The office of Indonesia's attorney general has formed a team to investigate the wealth of present and former Indonesian government officials, a spokesman of the office said here Tuesday.
JAKARTA, November 18 (Xinhua) -- The Indonesian National Land Agency's Jambi office has uncovered evidence of former President Soeharto's allegedly ill-gotten wealth in Central Sumatra Province alone, The Jakarta Post reported Wednesday.
JAKARTA, November 13 (Xinhua) -- In an apparent response to mounting demands from students and opposition groups, Indonesian legislators on Friday agreed to launch an investigation into former president Soeharto's wealth.

